<p id="Par25" class="p">We explore contributions for the case of linear risk curves (Fig. 
 <xref rid="Fig5" ref-type="fig" class="xref">5a</xref>) and their effects on contributions with respect to 1–4 round games (Figs. 
 <xref rid="Fig1" ref-type="fig" class="xref">1</xref>–
 <xref rid="Fig5" ref-type="fig" class="xref">5</xref>) and an 8 round game (Supplementary Fig. 
 <xref rid="MOESM1" ref-type="media" class="xref">2</xref>).
